From bf2c652488286181f3548512e4940e2b1b1078a8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jagan Teki <jagan@amarulasolutions.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Dec 2019 18:52:27 +0530
Subject: drm/sun4i: dsi: Add Allwinner A64 MIPI DSI support
Git-commit: 52028bfcb2330189c5e4ab943b3530b2117b8525
Patch-mainline: v5.6-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

The MIPI DSI controller in Allwinner A64 is similar to A33.

But unlike A33, A64 doesn't have DSI_SCLK gating so add compatible
for Allwinner A64 with uninitialized has_mod_clk driver.

Signed-off-by: Jagan Teki <jagan@amarulasolutions.com>
Tested-by: Merlijn Wajer <merlijn@wizzup.org>
Signed-off-by: Maxime Ripard <maxime@cerno.tech>
Link: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/20191222132229.30276-6-jagan@amarulasolutions.com
Signed-off-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/sun4i/sun6i_mipi_dsi.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/sun4i/sun6i_mipi_dsi.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/sun4i/sun6i_mipi_dsi.c
index cdfec03bf1a4..a75fcb113172 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/sun4i/sun6i_mipi_dsi.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/sun4i/sun6i_mipi_dsi.c
@@ -1256,6 +1256,7 @@ static const struct dev_pm_ops sun6i_dsi_pm_ops = {
 
 static const struct of_device_id sun6i_dsi_of_table[] = {
 	{ .compatible = "allwinner,sun6i-a31-mipi-dsi" },
+	{ .compatible = "allwinner,sun50i-a64-mipi-dsi" },
 	{ }
 };
 MODULE_DEVICE_TABLE(of, sun6i_dsi_of_table);
